## ğŸ“¦ 1. `lucide-react`

**Purpose**: Adds **beautiful icons** to your app (like buttons, navbars, cards).

ğŸ” Based on Lucide â€” an open-source fork of Feather icons.

âœ… Example usage:

```jsx
